item.title: CVE-2019-6531|2024-08-04T20:23:21.405Z -- kunbus -- pr100088%20modbus%20gateway
item.description: An attacker could retrieve passwords from a HTTP GET request from the Kunbus PR100088 Modbus gateway versions prior to Release R02 (or Software Version 1.1.13166) if the attacker is in an MITM position.
